{"tid":237764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"借刀殺人！中國要新疆穆斯林用APP互相檢舉","createTime":"2017-05-10T14:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T02:37:58.000Z","uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8baf1f4ea7e31fccb54564c40d7a2a22e60f39db","tid":237764,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:55:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">借刀殺人！中國要新疆穆斯林用APP互相檢舉<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php57jJGI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php57jJGI.jpg&h=7231e527&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在新疆，隨時有武警或執法人員監控一舉一動。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國為鎮壓新疆穆斯林花招百出，除了蓄鬍、穿長袍都被視為「極端象徵」外，所有移動車輛都要裝上GPS，還要民眾下載官方APP來作維安舉報。一名新疆的司機表示：「一個社區就像一個水果一樣，如果你用力擠壓，就會擠破。」<br />\n<br />\n根據《BBC中文網》，中國於3月30宣布在新疆維吾爾自治區進行，「去極端化政策」，一系列的禁令如不正常蓄鬍、禁止穿長袍、佩戴極端化標誌以及排斥或拒絕收看電視廣播等，以及民眾必須先上繳護照，出國前必須由官方審查，若觸犯將有刑事責任。之後又頒布了新政策，部分地區的活動車輛必須裝上GPS，另外中國也於新疆首都烏魯木齊設置了手機APP，讓民眾互相舉報協助維安。<br />\n<br />\n最新一期的《經濟學人》批判中國此種侮辱穆斯林的行為，文章表示中國用非常理的方式去侮辱穆斯林。文章引用一名新疆司機的話，「一個社區就像一個水果一樣，如果你用力擠壓，就會擠破。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php9np3N0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php9np3N0.jpg&h=10e032bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前在新疆留鬍子將被視為「極端象徵」。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2061421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2061421&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TajPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=72db6d5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2061421&h=b37b4641\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2061421</a>"},{"pid":"b7968af3a3275ab472b24a832e6f766ee3801460","tid":237764,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:57:57.000Z","msg":"新時代留髮不留頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9458649dcb47709c44e22ab665f4adee1aa2c5e8","tid":237764,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:59:15.000Z","msg":"I love big brother"},{"pid":"b3b2fad5ca82704fae8ec9f83f92a7486d200584","tid":237764,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:06:04.000Z","msg":"掩耳盜鈴"},{"pid":"d582e1bf45595c3bf4c65247aacf2610dabee849","tid":237764,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74b147ecebd5be59c364e733fde9df6c0b49920","tid":237764,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:33:09.000Z","msg":"中央請郁埋香港d南亞佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934bf4c8b0cfcac6bf78f1e630315792ff1ebb27","tid":237764,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:13:49.000Z","msg":"如果強制完全漢化佢哋會點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38181c1002393c427d9c1ffb94a913fd14381588","tid":237764,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:37:21.000Z","msg":"支持歐洲仿照。歐洲很多呢啲人，但又太多大愛"},{"pid":"39ed7d41c1eb2fa6b9d49bc4c9acee42cef4101f","tid":237764,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T02:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}